response.overview: It is a war of wills: A captured Pakistan-sponsored terrorist swears he will destroy the country while a police commissioner (in whose custody the terrorist is) will not leave any stone unturned to stop the menace that the terrorist is going to unleash from behind the high security prison. A war of words follows between the two strongmen and the stage is set to prove their talents.
response.title: Commissioner Narasimha Naidu
